Package: FBMS
Type: Package
Title: Flexible Bayesian Model Selection and Model Averaging
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-09-30
Encoding: UTF-8
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jon", "Lachmann", email = "jon@lachmann.nu", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Aliaksandr", "Hubin", email = "aliaksah@math.uio.no", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Implements the MJMCMC (Mode Jumping MCMC) described in Hubin and Storvik 2018 <doi:10.1016/j.csda.2018.05.020>
and GMJMCMC (Genetically Modified MJMCMC) described in Hubin et al. <doi:10.1613/jair.1.13047> algorithms as well as the
subsampling counterpart described in Lachmann et al. <doi:10.1016/j.ijar.2022.08.018> for Flexible Bayesian Model Selection and Model Averaging.
License: GPL-2
